## Tasks Collection [/tasks]

Collection of all `Tasks`.

### List All Tasks [GET]

+ Parameters
    + appKey (string) - `appKey` of your Auvo's account.
    + token (string) - `token` of your Auvo's account.
    + startDate (string) - Initial date of the searched tasks
    + endDate (string) - Final date of the searched tasks
    + idUserTo (optional, number) - `userId` of the `User` responsable for the task
    + onlyFinishedAll (optional, boolean) - All finished tasks, including manually and automatically finished tasks
    + onlyFinishedAutomatically (optional, boolean) - Automatically finished tasks
    + onlyFinishedManually (optional, boolean) - Manually finished tasks
    + onlyNotFinished (optional, boolean) - Not finished tasks
    + customerId (optional, number) - `customerId` of the `Customer` related to the task
    + teamId (optional, number) - `teamId` of the `Team` that is assigned for the task
    + taskType (optional, number) - `typeId` of the `Task Type` related to the task
    + flatTask (optional, boolean) - This attribute will force a flat response, the following fields will not be sent in the response: Images, Attachments and Questionnaires
    + lastUpdated (optional, string) - Only tasks updated after this date will be listed, it includes updates in the task an the questionnaires inside the task, this field allows sincronization scripts to work with a lightweight response for general update tasks
    + imagesAsUrl (optional, boolean) - The images and attachments will be sent as URL's, not in base64 format, it reduces the load in the response ant consequently the response time
    
+ Response 200
    
    + Body
            
            [
                {
                    "taskId": "23",
                    "idUserFrom": 123,
                    "idUserTo": 123,
                    "customerId": 456,
                    "creationDate": "2016-03-23T14:10:35",
